.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, family, romance, sports
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: tulip, bellflower, iris, begonia, amaryllis, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | romance | disaster | sports | family     | drama  |
| Flower           | iris | bellflower    | tulip      | balloon-flower  | begonia | amaryllis |

