.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, disco, dubstep, indie
6 different pets are kept: bird, dog, pony, guinea-pig, horse, ferret
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the fan of country is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the owner of the ferret is the fan of disco##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the pony is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | disco | blues      | classical  | indie | dubstep |
| Pet     | bird | ferret  | horse | pony | guinea-pig  | dog    |

