.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, hiking, singing, traveling, woodworking
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, aconite, zinnia, azalea, orchid, poppy
 1. the person who growszinnia is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | baking | traveling | filmmaking | hiking  |
| Flower   | poppy  | azalea  | zinnia  | daisy | orchid      | aconite |

