The people have 6 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, puzzles, drawing, hiking, singing
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
9. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep    | country | indie     | disco   | folk     |
| Hobby   | hiking | sudoku | singing | puzzles | drawing | reading |

