2. the person who likes white is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes coral##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up     | juice | almond-milk | lemonade | mirinda   |
| Color        | amber | coral | turquise | emerald   | white    | lilac |

