1. the person eating lemon is on the left of the craftsman house##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
3. the person eating lemon is the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person eating onion is the modern house##1
6. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
7. the palace house is the person eating pineapple##1
8. the craftsman house is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
9. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |
| Food        | lemon     | peach | grapes   | onion      | pineapple | grapefruit |
| House   | gothic-revival | craftsman  | victorian | modern | palace   | farmhouse     |

