.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, funk, house, metal, rock, salsa
City: new-york, colone, venice, liverpool, miami, berlin
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
9. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
| City     | berlin  | new-york | colone | liverpool | miami  | venice |

 